हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Childhood promises bind Tara and Aditya, two lost souls torn apart by fate. Sixteen years later, Tara now a powerful CEO searches endlessly for the boy who once protected her, while Aditya, burdened by betrayal and amnesia, fights to reclaim his identity. Between Jatin’s cunning schemes, Jiya’s manipulative love, and a highstakes corporate game of power and deception, their story unfolds a battle of love, lies, and strategy. Watch Now!
